(- 2 in / 2 out: ~615 vB) Tj
T*
(- 3 in / 2 out: ~664 vB) Tj
T*
(- Throughput Formulas) Tj
T*
(Let:) Tj
T*
(- Bv = 2,500,000 effective vbytes per block cap) Tj
T*
(- T = 120 seconds) Tj
T*
(- Savg = average non-coinbase tx vsize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then:) Tj
T*
(- tx_per_block = Bv / Savg) Tj
T*
(- TPS = tx_per_block / T) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Examples:) Tj
T*
(- Savg=566 -> ~36.8 TPS) Tj
T*
(- Savg=615 -> ~33.9 TPS) Tj
T*
(- Savg=664 -> ~31.4 TPS) Tj
T*
(- Post-Tail Net Supply Math) Tj
T*
(At full block utilization by vbytes:) Tj
T*
(- Total fee floor capacity per block = 2,500,000 * 225 = 562,500,000 atoms = 0.5625 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Annual total fees at full utilization = 147,825 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Burnable routed share \(80%\) at full utilization = 118,260 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Post-tail net annual change:) Tj
T*
(- Delta_supply = 65,700 - \(118,260 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deflation threshold:) Tj
T*
(- utilization ~= 65,700 / 118,260 ~= 0.5556 \(55.56%\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Interpretation:) Tj
T*
(- <55.56% utilization: inflationary net.) Tj
T*
(- =55.56%: neutral net.) Tj
T*
(- >55.56%: deflationary net \(subject to floor clipping\).) Tj
T*
(- Coinbase Invariants) Tj
T*
(Consensus payout invariants:) Tj
T*
(- coinbase_outputs_sum_atoms == block_reward_atoms + fees_miner_atoms) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When fee routing is active, blocks carry auditable fields:) Tj
T*
(- fees_total_atoms) Tj
T*
(- fees_miner_atoms) Tj
T*
(- fees_burned_atoms) Tj
T*
(- fees_pool_atoms) Tj
T*
(- cumulative_burned_atoms) Tj
T*
(- Consensus Change Reminder) Tj
T*
(Changing any of the following is consensus-breaking and requires coordinated upgrade:) Tj
T*
(- reward schedule,) Tj
T*
(- tail reward,) Tj
T*
(- fee uplift/routing percents,) Tj
T*
(- burn split and floor,) Tj
T*
(- fee constants,) Tj
T*
(- atom denomination.) Tj
T*
